---
<section id="why-choose-us" class="section-padding bg-white">
  <div class="container-custom">
    <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black text-primary mb-4">Why Choose Us?</h2>
      <div class="w-20 h-1.5 bg-secondary mx-auto mb-6"></div>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 font-medium leading-relaxed">
        Dedicated to protecting your most significant investment. Our commitment to quality and transparency sets us apart.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 text-center">
      <div class="p-6 rounded-xl border border-gray-100 shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow duration-300">
        <div class="text-4xl text-secondary mb-4 flex justify-center">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-award">
            <circle cx="12" cy="8" r="7"/>
            <polyline points="8.21 13.89 7 22 12 18 17 22 15.79 13.89"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-primary mb-2">Decades of Expertise</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600">Over 20 years of experience in Singapore's construction and renovation industry.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="p-6 rounded-xl border border-gray-100 shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow duration-300">
        <div class="text-4xl text-secondary mb-4 flex justify-center">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-eye">
            <path d="M2 12s3-7 10-7 10 7 10 7-3 7-10 7-10-7-10-7Z"/>
            <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-primary mb-2">Meticulous Detail</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600">We catch what others miss—from hollow tiles to hidden water seepage.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="p-6 rounded-xl border border-gray-100 shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow duration-300">
        <div class="text-4xl text-secondary mb-4 flex justify-center">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-file-text">
            <path d="M15 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V7Z"/>
            <path d="M14 2v4a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h4"/>
            <path d="M10 9H8"/>
            <path d="M16 13H8"/>
            <path d="M16 17H8"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-primary mb-2">BCA Standards</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600">Our inspections follow strict BCA CONQUAS guidelines for professional quality.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
